text:
Both of you,
want to take a little break?

...Producer-san,
yeah, let's take a short break.

That's good.
I brought some snacks.
Well, feel free to have some!

Thank you.
My throat was just getting dry.

I think I'll pass on the onigiri for now.
It might make me feel heavy.

Is that so?
Then, please have it after we're done.

A meat bun, huh?
Even though it's scorching hot from all the dancing...!?

Oh, right.
I guess something else would've been better...!
